		 <h2>What we do and what we don't do</h2>
		 <p>We don't tweet daily and we are not spam. We do not post to your account without your permission. When you sign up you're asked to opt in for us to tweet your top 5 followers list, only if you select that will we tweet your list. You can remove our app anytime at Twitter.com-&gt;Settings-&gt;Apps-&gt;Top5Followers-&gt;Revoke Access.</p>
		 <p>We use our own algorithm to find your top 5 followers on Twitter. We find your top 5 followers based on the number of retweets, the number of favorites and the number of replies to your recent tweets by your followers.</p> 
